14.9 We recommended that Management:
a. Exert more effort in looking for a suitable site for an ESL;
b. Expand the coverage of collection of residual waste to cover all the
barangays of the municipality by appropriating funds for the
purchase of additional garbage truck and hiring of additional
drivers/workers to augment the existing manpower;
